1.We have relied upon the estimates given by the management in case of costs other than construction cost.We also relied on Mobile No.AFS Date,KYC Type and KYC Number given by promoter.As the Data is ready upto 24-08-2020 we have considered till that date.Wherever Date of agreement for sale not available and direct sale deed made we have considered sale deed date.					
2.The preparation of the accompanying Statement is the responsibility of the Management of the Company. This responsibility includes designing, implementing and maintaining internal control relevant to the preparation and presentation of the Statement, and applying an appropriate basis of preparation; and making estimates that are reasonable in the circumstances.					
3.We conducted our examination of the Statement in accordance with the Guidance Note on Reports or Certificates for Special Purposes issued by the Institute of Chartered Accountants of India. The Guidance Note requires that we comply with the ethical requirements of the Code of Ethics issued by the Institute of Chartered Accountants of India.					
4. The certificate is addressed to and provided to the promoters of the project  solely for the purpose to enable comply with requirement of RERA , and should not be used by any other person or for any other purpose. Accordingly, we do not accept or assume any liability or any duty of care for any other purpose or to any other person to whom this certificate is shown or into whose hands it may come without our prior consent in writing.					
5..The deposit made in RERA Account consist of Deposit Received from buyer as well as Unsecured Loans shown in current liablity.The Taxes includes payment made in cash as well as utilisation of credit.The separate RERA Account is not opened in line with the RERA Guildelines by promoter.In the absence of Separate Account we are not able to clearly bifurcate how much amount is utilised for Construction purpose and hence we have consider total withdrawl.For Shop no 113 to 128 sale deed executed on 24-08-2020 but as the entiries in books not made we have not considering in inventory sold.In th e absence of RERA Bank Statement we have considered Balance as Per Books which is subject to reconciliation with Actual Bank transactions.
